Verifies the CRC8 checksum of a message.

detaileddescription.para: This function calculates the expected CRC8 checksum of the input message and compares it to the last byte of the message to verify its integrity.

parameterdescription.para: Length of the message in bytes.

simplesect.para: true if the CRC8 checksum matches the last byte of the message, false otherwise.

briefdescription.para: Set the last byte of a message to a CRC8 checksum.

detaileddescription.para: This function calculates the CRC8 checksum of the input message and sets it as the last byte of the message.

parameterdescription.para: Length of the message in bytes.

simplesect.para: true if the CRC8 checksum is successfully set as the last byte, false otherwise.

briefdescription.para: Verifies the CRC16 checksum of a message.

detaileddescription.para: This function calculates the expected CRC16 checksum of the input message and compares it to the last two bytes of the message to verify its integrity.

parameterdescription.para: Length of the message in bytes.

simplesect.para: true if the CRC16 checksum matches the last two bytes of the message, false otherwise.

briefdescription.para: Set the last two bytes of a message to a CRC16 checksum.

detaileddescription.para: This function calculates the CRC16 checksum of the input message and sets it as the last two bytes of the message.

parameterdescription.para: Length of the message in bytes.

simplesect.para: true if the CRC16 checksum is successfully set as the last two bytes, false otherwise.

briefdescription.para: Calculate and return the CRC8 checksum of a message.

detaileddescription.para: This function iterates through the input message and computes the CRC8 checksum using the provided CRC8 initialization value.

parameterdescription.para: Length of the message in bytes.
Initial CRC8 value to start the checksum calculation.

briefdescription.para: Calculate and return the CRC16 checksum of a message.

detaileddescription.para: This function iterates through the input message and computes the CRC16 checksum using the provided CRC16 initialization value.

parameterdescription.para: Length of the message in bytes.
Initial CRC16 value to start the checksum calculation.

simplesect.para: Calculated CRC16 checksum for the message.
